item.title: CVE-2023-48434|2024-09-13T15:02:46.639Z -- projectworlds%20pvt.%20limited -- online%20voting%20system%20project
item.description: Online Voting System Project v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Unauthenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'username' parameter of the reg_action.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.
